00:27:35,780 --> 00:27:36,840
the old-fashioned

652
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:38,860
nonrelativistic Lagrangian.

653
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:41,420
The old-fashioned nonrelativistic Lagrangian

654
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:46,200
